The paper discusses the challenges and techniques for intrusion detection, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses anomaly detection methods, which are often based on machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI, cs.LG). The paper also mentions Security Information and Event Management (SIEM) tools, which are used for monitoring and analyzing security-related events (cs.SI). Finally, the paper discusses the need for future research, which is often a topic in software engineering (cs.SE).
